def_cn: 不可触动的；不受影响的；碰不得的
def_en: If you say that someone is untouchable, you mean that they cannot be affected or punished in any way.

def_cn: 高人一等的；无与伦比的；无可匹敌的
def_en: If you describe someone, especially a sports player or entertainer, as untouchable, you are emphasizing that they are better than anyone else in what they do.

def_cn: 不可接触者，贱民（指印度社会最低阶层的人）
def_en: Some people refer to Hindus of the lowest social rank as untouchables .
